Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.40,0:23:07.74,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}つかんだこの絆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.74,0:23:11.41,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,500)}握りしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.61,0:23:14.87,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}準備好起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.61,0:23:14.87,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ready, ready ready for the take off
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.87,0:23:17.87,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}前往夢想所指之地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.87,0:23:17.87,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}夢が目指す場所へ
